## Research Data Attribution

The empirical data in this repository is compiled from multiple public sources:
- Bitcoin/Ethereum data: LSEG Datastream
- Energy consumption: Digiconomist, Cambridge CBECI
- Mining distribution: Cambridge Centre for Alternative Finance
- Electricity prices: IEA, national energy agencies

Users of this data should cite the original sources as appropriate.
